heatload 0.3:
		Malte Thoma takes over the project
		added comand-line options for

	 -d, --no_decoration      no decoration
	 -f X, --frame_size X     X = border-size sourounding boxes [5]
	 -h, --help               display this help message and exit
	 -l, --no_label           no numerical temp. and load display
	 -r X, --refresh X        X = refresh rate [1000]
	 -x X, --x_size X         X = x-size of meter [256]
	 -y X, --y_size X         X = y-size of meter [100]



